headline: It's Utility Scam Awareness Day and FirstEnergy Urges Customers to Stay On Guard Through the Winter Months
summary: In recognition of Utility Scam Awareness Day on Wednesday, Nov. 20, FirstEnergy Corp. (NYSE: FE) is offering tips to prevent the public from falling for common utility scams, especially as the cold winter months are fast approaching.
